Resistance.help: The Bruiser is a Brute. He has good resistance to Lethal and Smashing Damage and some resistance to Fire and Cold Damage. He is street wise and Their training makes them resistant to Confuse, Fear and Placate. His experience in the elements makes him slightly resistant to Fire, Cold and Toxic Damage. He can fire a Burst or a single heavy Slug from his Assault Rifle.
Resistance.shortHelp: Auto Res(Smashing, Lethal, Fire, Cold, Fear, Confuse, Placate)

Jab.help: A quick jab that deals minor damage, but has a chance of Disorienting the target, especially if coupled with other attacks. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Very Fast
